content: CompTIA is the leading provider of vendor-neutral IT certifications worldwide, and employers depend on CompTIA certifications to make smart hiring decisions. CompTIA helps IT professionals demonstrate their aptitude in various fields, such as security, network administration, computer repair and server administration.CompTIA helps you get the tech career you deserve with industry-leading certifications ! 50% OF THE PRICE !CompTIA IT Fundamentals (ITF+) (FC0-U61) CompTIA A+ (Exam 220-1101 or 220-1102)CompTIA Network+ (N10-008) CompTIA Security+ (SY0-601) CompTIA Cloud+ (CV0-003) CompTIA Linux+ (XK0-005) CompTIA Server+ (SK0-005) CompTIA Cybersecurity Analyst (CySA+) (CS0-003) CompTIA PenTest+ (PT0-002) CompTIA Data+ (DA0-001) CompTIA Cloud Essentials+ (CLO-002) CompTIA Project+ (PK0-005) Contact :Discord: comptia123 & Telegram: @takken22901FAQ*What's the ETA ?1-2 Day but the delay of reception can be more slow for people of this Country : American Samoa , Canada , Guam , Puerto Rico , U.S. Virgin Islands , United States , United States Minor Outlying Islands .* Can i pay after the reception ?Yes of course* The voucher are there from "blackhat" activity ?The vouchers are not generated by any blackhat activity
